{"tid":1772364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟日報旗下u magazine 今期有pepe 袋","createTime":"2019-12-06T14:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T16:12:16.000Z","uid":220144,"like":6,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2120ff0920472488399bb5fc56df16d2b46f05d8","tid":1772364,"uid":220144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:18:58.000Z","msg":"經濟日報集團（423）執行董事、《香港經濟日報》副社長石鏡泉，於上周六建制派「守護香港集會」中指，「教仔」須用藤條及水喉通。今早有網民於連登發帖指，「本身為廣告Agency，今早客戶打黎要立即On Hold或取消經濟日報集團旗下所有媒體的廣告，直至另行通知。我講大話死全家。」<br />\n<br />\n經濟日報集團旗下有四大業務，包括：<br />\n媒體業務&mdash;香港經濟日報、晴報、U Magazine、e-zone、iMoney、經濟日報出版社、泰業印刷、悅友<br />\n財經通訊社、資訊及軟件業務&mdash;經濟通、交易通、環富通<br />\n招聘廣告及培訓業務&mdash;CTgoodjobs、經濟商學院<br />\n生活網站&mdash;樂本．健、U Lifestyle（U Travel、港生活、U Beauty、U Food）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGXgotZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGXgotZ.png&h=740e30c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地唔係仲買呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb72bf05972e5c0a6a8150dcd83949fe18848d6","tid":1772364,"uid":220144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:19:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96c68d0dea918c3603cd945484536c45567757f9","tid":1772364,"uid":59863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:21:06.000Z","msg":"原來PePe 都有香港代理版權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9494f29cd62fe40a530d795f45f333bc0b505fc1","tid":1772364,"uid":220144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179d844d5aadd4a1f8edeba1132579c6fb07e20e","tid":1772364,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:24:04.000Z","msg":"經濟日報。不了"},{"pid":"e33a396a8d14f3780b3e7095be8950bde1514b32","tid":1772364,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:25:41.000Z","msg":"估唔到"},{"pid":"79a9f3eba976f11a248c87b419a9cd4586c1e725","tid":1772364,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:26:59.000Z","msg":"死鏡泉辭左職"},{"pid":"fe29e61ca4e3a483e126cdde926928299f62e559","tid":1772364,"uid":220144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:56:44.000Z","msg":"7月23日，香港經濟日報集團宣布，石鏡泉22日向董事會辭任集團執行董事及集團刊物《香港經濟日報》副社長，董事會23日批准並即時生效。石鏡泉將繼續擔任集團專欄作家。<br />\n<br />\n現年71歲的石鏡泉，為《香港經濟日報》創辦人，離職前為該報副社長及研究部主管。根據《香港經濟日報》最新年報，截至今年3月31日，石鏡泉持有集團0.232%股份，以7月23日收市價計算，其股份市值約162萬。另外，作為集團執行董事的石鏡泉2018/19年度總薪金及福利為346萬，當中包括296.6萬的薪金、34.6萬酌情花紅及14.8萬僱主退休金供款。<br />\n<br />\n另外，集團同年度亦向石鏡泉支付6.7萬顧問版權費及25.3萬撰稿人酬金。<br />\n<br />\n721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就唔買啦"},{"pid":"ecc9f5f159fb9dab7b0e48a2401643aa99591675","tid":1772364,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T15:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好糾結"},{"pid":"c1240734e1736a00e4c5e22eabf08341f3578ab3","tid":1772364,"uid":139129,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"96c68d0dea918c3603cd945484536c45567757f9","tid":1772364,"uid":59863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:21:06.000Z","msg":"原來PePe 都有香港代理版權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:21:26.000Z","msg":"係呀！坊間所有二次創作三次創作全部一蚊都冇俾返個原作者！本身pepe只係一隻普通嘅卡通人物, 隻青蛙俾人咁樣用法，又有冇尊重過版權問題？"},{"pid":"b9929e511c6e371f30b018c5483c3d2635c5733b","tid":1772364,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"推屌佢老母"},{"pid":"902827acb4006556b390d96d009378129cf6ea4b","tid":1772364,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry